OL,3,CRecyclables to go in one bin under
OL,4,Csimpler collection rules
OL,6,FHouseholds in England will be able to
OL,7,Fput recyclables in one bin under
OL,8,Fsimpler collection rules, the
OL,9,Fgovernment has announced.
OL,11,FThe Environment Department (Defra)
OL,12,Fannounced on Thursday that the same
OL,13,Fmaterials will be collected from
OL,14,Fhomes, workplaces and schools across
OL,15,Fthe country in order to end the
OL,16,Fconfusion caused by councils operating
OL,17,Fdifferent systems.
