OL,3,CRecyclables to go in one bin under
OL,4,Csimpler collection rules
OL,6,FUnder the new rules, people will be
OL,7,Fable to put plastic, metal, glass,
OL,8,Fpaper and card in one bin. Councils
OL,9,Fwill also be able to co-collect food
OL,10,Fand garden waste.
OL,12,FDefra said the new measures will mean
OL,13,Fhouseholds no longer have to check
OL,14,Fwhich materials their specific council
OL,15,Fwill accept for recycling.
OL,17,FThey will also reduce complexity for
OL,18,Fwaste collectors and boost recycling
OL,19,Frates, it added.
