OL,3,CRecyclables to go in one bin under
OL,4,Csimpler collection rules
OL,6,FElsewhere, the government said it is
OL,7,Fsupporting councils to increase the
OL,8,Ffrequency of collections in a bid to
OL,9,Fprevent bins from cluttering streets.
OL,11,FA minimum backstop will be introduced
OL,12,Fso that councils are expected to
OL,13,Fcollect black bin waste at least
OL,14,Ffortnightly, alongside weekly food
OL,15,Fwaste collections, it announced.
OL,17,FRecycling Minister Robbie Moore said a
OL,18,F"patchwork" of different bin
OL,19,Fcollections across England means it
OL,20,Fcan be hard to know what your council
OL,21,Fwill accept.
