OL,3,CRecyclables to go in one bin under
OL,4,Csimpler collection rules
OL,6,F"Our plans for Simpler Recycling will
OL,7,Fend that confusion: ensuring that the
OL,8,Fsame set of materials will be
OL,9,Fcollected regardless of where you
OL,10,Flive," he added.
OL,12,FPaul Vanston, chief executive of the
OL,13,FIndustry Council for Packaging and the
OL,14,FEnvironment (INCPEN), said households
OL,15,Fcan take this government announcement
OL,16,Fas a pledge that local councils all
OL,17,Fover the country "will all speedily
OL,18,Fimplement recycling collections of the
OL,19,Ffull range of materials that will
OL,20,Fmatch on-pack recycling labels
OL,21,Fcitizens rely on for guidance".
