OL,6,FDefra said the plans will apply to all
OL,7,Fhomes in England, including flats.
OL,9,FSimilar measures will apply to non-
OL,10,Fhousehold premises, including
OL,11,Fbusinesses, hospitals, schools and
OL,12,Funiversities and places of worship.
